description:
Sorry everyone, this episode didn't turn out as nice as I hoped it would. I was experimenting with editing and voice over commentary. Silly me, thinking my voice couldn't possibly get any more monotone than it normally is... but I guess 2 am is not the time to be recording. (3:30 am after editing x_X)

Anyway, thanks everyone for your support over this last year. You are all so awesome!
